OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain is
OL,6,Fexpected to clear northeast through
OL,7,Fthe evening, this turning heavy for a
OL,8,Ftime. Then staying dry overnight with
OL,9,Fvariable cloud and clear spells.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FQuite cloudy to start but
OL,12,Fthis soon breaking up through the
OL,13,Fmorning. Staying dry and warm with
OL,14,Fprolonged bright or sunny spells
OL,15,Fthrough the day.
